 The UI of the app has the following elements:

- A search bar at the top with a magnifying glass icon on the left and a cross icon on the right.
- Left sidebar with 6 sections: My Explorer, Favorites, On This Mac, Collections, How-tos and App Guides.
- A breadcrumb trail at the top of the main content area, showing the user's current location in the app.
- A large preview image of the selected app in the main content area.
- A set of buttons below the preview image that allow the user to open the app, view its details, or share it.
- A list of other apps in the main content area, below the preview image and the buttons.
- A progress bar at the bottom of the window that shows the status of the current operation.
- A gear icon in the bottom-right corner that opens the app's settings.